{"type": "article", "id": 10557, "title": "Protrude悬浮托盘", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-09T07:16:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606142308xYbLB0czy6Ft47Rr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>来自东京的 </span><span>YOY </span><span>设计事务所，他们创造的主题倾向于在空间与物体之间创作出新的故事。这个木质托盘大部分都是处于悬浮状态，虽然看起来要掉下去，但永远不会。你可以在里面放些 </span><span>A4 </span><span>大小的纸张、文件，也可以放杯咖啡等等。其实借助的是底部有架子可以将托盘固定到任何你喜欢的角度。这种视觉差还是挺酷的。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142306pE16uKL27PZwTB48.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142307ylaKjQq02YXGoxZe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142307BHGt9eKnYPIyvzjS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142308nr2E1JBs8WogpckY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}